## 1. Default Loading Model

- load global core first
- use `roles/developer.md` unless the task clearly matches another role-pack
- then load the matching stack-pack

Common mappings:
- frontend/UI/desktop -> `roles/developer.md` + `{{FORGE_HOME}}/stacks/frontend.md`
- Java/Spring -> `roles/developer.md` + `{{FORGE_HOME}}/stacks/java.md`
- Python/FastAPI/Django -> `roles/developer.md` + `{{FORGE_HOME}}/stacks/python.md`
- PM work -> `{{FORGE_HOME}}/roles/product-manager.md` + `{{FORGE_HOME}}/stacks/product.md`
- UI design work -> `{{FORGE_HOME}}/roles/ui-designer.md` + `{{FORGE_HOME}}/stacks/design.md`
- architecture work -> `{{FORGE_HOME}}/roles/solution-architect.md` + `{{FORGE_HOME}}/stacks/architecture.md`
- QA work -> `{{FORGE_HOME}}/roles/qa-strategist.md` + `{{FORGE_HOME}}/stacks/qa.md`
- release/devex work -> `{{FORGE_HOME}}/roles/release-devex.md` + `{{FORGE_HOME}}/stacks/release.md`

